WEBVTT

00:00:01.142 --> 00:00:02.897
So, my name is Roger Doiron,

00:00:02.921 --> 00:00:05.342
and I have a subversive plot.

00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:07.618
(Laughter)

00:00:07.642 --> 00:00:08.946
(Applause)

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:11.320
It is so subversive, in fact,

00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:15.468
that it has the potential
to radically alter the balance of power,

00:00:15.492 --> 00:00:17.547
not only in our own country,

00:00:17.571 --> 00:00:19.008
but in the entire world.

00:00:19.824 --> 00:00:21.379
Now I realize, I'm sounding --

00:00:21.403 --> 00:00:22.416
(Laughter)

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:25.196
a little bit like Dr. Evil now.

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:26.392
I understand that.

00:00:26.416 --> 00:00:29.202
But trust me -- we have very,
very little in common.

00:00:29.226 --> 00:00:32.887
His plots are all about
destruction and secrecy,